            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "taprati",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ") of multitudes of men.” And of his temple of Nergal he says: “The house of Nergal, within the city of Tarbiçu, I caused to be made, and like day I caused it to shine” (",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "usnammir",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ")",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
